---js
const eleventyNavigation = {
	key: "Home",
	order: 1
};

const numberOfLatestPostsToShow = 3;

---
<div class="content-box-inner">
	<h1>Hello, world</h1>
	<div class="portrait">
		<img alt="Line drawing portrait of a person with long dark hair and glasses." src="../img/portrait.svg">
	</div>
	<p>
		<span>I am Dr. Samuel R. Mendez, a researcher and artist focused on media, technology, and science communication. I recently got my PhD in public health from Harvard. And I have a background in media arts and media studies. I aim to support better science communication online. I do that through research, teaching, and media technology. Here are some highlights:</span>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<a href="https://doi.org/10.2196/59786">A study of public health agencies using Twitter</a>, from 2012 through 2022.
			</li>
			<li>
				<a href="https://hsph.harvard.edu/research/health-communication/resources/digital-safety-kit-for-public-health/">Digital Safety Kit for Public Health</a>: A guide to decrease the harm of online harassment.
			</li>
			<li>
				<a href="https://bsky.app/profile/samuelanimates.bsky.social/feed/aaaarylo7rb2e">"Public Health 🛟" feed on BlueSky</a>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</p>	
	
	{% set postsCount = collections.posts | length %}
	{% set latestPostsCount = postsCount | min(numberOfLatestPostsToShow) %}
	<h2> Check out my latest {{ latestPostsCount }} blog posts </h2>
	<p>Here are some of my latest thoughts on media, tech, and communication:</p>
	{% set postslist = collections.posts | head(-1 * numberOfLatestPostsToShow) %}
	{% set postslistCounter = postsCount %}
	{% include "postslist.njk" %}

	<h2> Follow me </h2>
	<p>To connect with a growing network in public health, follow my <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/samuelanimates.bsky.social/feed/aaaarylo7rb2e">public health BlueSky feed</a>. To join a community of researchers and advocates on social media, use my <a href="https://bsky.app/starter-pack/samuelanimates.bsky.social/3kw5z4vfc3h2m">"Public Health BlueSky" starter pack</a></p>
	
	<p>
		<span>For more updates from me:</span>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@samuelanimates">YouTube</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/newsletters/health-literacy-right-now-7110314537236463616/">"Health Literacy Right Now" newsletter</a> on LinkedIn
			</li>
			<li>
				<a href="https://bsky.app/profile/samuelanimates.bsky.social">BlueSky</a>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</p>
</div>